snippet.title: Best VGM 2418 - Magical Tetris Challenge - Big Bad Wolf's Theme
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1591 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UWOTB6x_WAs

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Arcade / N64 / Playstation
Magical Tetris Challenge (1998)
Big Bad Wolf's Theme
Masato Kouda
